&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;In 2011/12, an estimated 82.7% of non-frequent bus services in England ran on time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
