&lt;h2 id="notes"&gt;Notes&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3 id="operating-costs"&gt;Operating costs&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(a) These data are based on each operator’s statutory accounts. Any figures relating to premia or associated payments to the Department for Transport or passenger transport executives are excluded.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(b) For each operator, the latest available statutory accounts have been used. As indicated above, the periods covered by each set of accounts do not always match. Because of this, it is not appropriate to sum up each item to derive a total cost.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(c) Although we have aimed to be as consistent as possible, operators may not treat all aspects of operating costs in the same way in their accounts, and so care should be taken when using these figures.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id="network-grant"&gt;Network Grant&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(d) This is calculated by taking the total network grant in 2010-11, and allocating it to each franchise based on their share of fixed track access charges.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="background-information"&gt;Background information&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The ‘operating cost’ column shows the costs incurred by each Train Operating Company (TOC) associated with running their services; this is based on operators’ statutory accounts, and excludes any premia or subsidy. Within this total are payments made by operators to Network Rail for access to the rail network which contribute towards infrastructure costs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The ‘Allocated Network Grant’ column, allocates, to each operator, the grant paid by the Department for Transport to Network Rail in 2010-11. The grant effectively pays the infrastructure costs incurred by Network Rail that are not covered by operators. In the table above, each operator is allocated a share of the grant in proportion to their fixed track access charge.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3 id="the-following-file-contains-these-figures-for-each-of-the-dft-franchised-train-operators"&gt;The following file contains these figures for each of the DfT franchised train operators:&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;cost of rail network CSV file&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;publishing schedule: annually&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;last updated: 31 October 2012&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;next update: December 2012&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Further information about this indicator can be found in the measurement template.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="further-information"&gt;Further information&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/department-for-transport-business-plan"&gt;Business Plan 2012-2015&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
