    <updated>2011-05-29T00:00:00+01:00</updated>
    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/cost-of-maintaining-the-highways-agency-s-motorway-and-a-road-network-per-lane-mile"/>
    <title>Cost of maintaining the Highways Agency’s motorway and A road network per lane mile</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;h2 id="dft-business-plan-input-indicator"&gt;DfT Business Plan input indicator&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3 id="geographical-coverage-england"&gt;Geographical coverage: England&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h3 id="information-broken-down-by-region"&gt;Information broken down by: Region&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h2 id="latest-data"&gt;Latest data&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The cost of operating the Strategic Road Network for 2011-12 was 0.3 pence per vehicle mile, unchanged from the 2010-11 out turn figure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Cost of maintaining the Highways Agency motorway and A road network per lane mile – Maintenance cost per lane mile (£k)&lt;/p&gt;

