    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/households-with-good-transport-access-to-key-services-or-work"/>
    <title>Households with good transport access to key services or work</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;h2 id="dft-business-plan-input-indicator"&gt;DfT Business Plan input indicator&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;h3 id="geographical-coverage-england"&gt;Geographical coverage: England&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h3 id="information-broken-down-by-local-authorities-urban-and-rural-areas-and-regions"&gt;Information broken down by: Local authorities, urban and rural areas, and regions&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;h2 id="latest-data"&gt;Latest data&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The index accessibility score for England in 2011 was 97&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Most recent data&lt;/th&gt;
